    "## The Solution: BigCompany Inc.'s Expense Approval Agent\n",
    "\n",
    "Here's the workflow the engineering team designed:\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Employee submits expense\n",
    "        │\n",
    "        ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────┐\n",
    "│Classify Expense │ ◄── AI categorizes and checks policy\n",
    "└────────┬────────┘\n",
    "         │\n",
    "    ┌────┴────┐\n",
    "    │ Amount? │\n",
    "    └────┬────┘\n",
    "         │\n",
    "   ┌─────┴──────┐\n",
    "   │             │\n",
    "   ▼             ▼\n",
    "≤ $500        > $500\n",
    "(auto)       (needs human)\n",
    "   │             │\n",
    "   │         ┌───┴─────┐\n",
    "   │         │ PAUSE   │\n",
    "   │         │interrupt│ ◄── Human reviews\n",
    "   │         └───┬─────┘\n",
    "   │             │\n",
    "   ▼             ▼\n",
    "┌─────────────────┐\n",
    "│Process Decision │ ◄── Approve or reject\n",
    "└────────┬────────┘\n",
    "         │\n",
    "         ▼\n",
    "       END\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "The key feature: **small expenses are auto-approved**, but **large expenses pause for human review**. Let's build it!"
